item.description: About Hi, my name is Duc. I am a Software Development Fresher at ZaloPay. I am also a third-year student at Ho Chi Minh City University of Technology - Vietnam National University, majoring in Computer Science. I’m an ambitious problem solver with a passion for software development. I’m eager to learn new things which will help the team in which I will work to meet its milestones. I have some experiences in ReactJS, Express.
